ActJobs, Growth and Long-term Prosperity Act
SubjectOrder Fixing September 24, 2014 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing September 24, 2014, as the day on which sections 157 and 158 and subsections 159(2) and (4), 160(1), (3) and (4) and 161(2) and (3) of the Jobs, Growth and Long-term Prosperity Act, chapter 19 of the Statutes of Canada, 2012, COME INTO FORCE.
